name: Tubu Internet Solutions
tag_list: web-hosting, domains, domain-registration, hosting, registrar, web, web-services
overview:
Tubu Internet Solutions (LLC) is a hometown kind of a web hosting a domain registration company. Their focus is on giving second to none services to their customers. The company was founded on the idea that no-one should be forced to pay top-dollar for web services.

Tubu Internet Solutions was founded in 1999 with one mission in mind - to bring the advantages of the internet to everyone. Over the years the company has grown and the range of clientele has broadened. We offer services to fire companies, schools, private organizations, clubs, individuals, churches, youth groups and so much more. We’re a family oriented company with our clients’ interests at heart. If they need it done - we do it, and with a minimum of hassle. Tubu Internet Solutions is a Pittsburgh based Web hosting company - your total hosting solution.
